- Some weapons are marked as |cffffcc00[two hand weapon]|r, It means greater damage bonus than other of similar level but a penalization of 161 Agility.|n- New advanced stats like Fortune or Constitution work better on high levels (50+).|n- Lethal attack bonus is stackable with all kind of damage dealed, it means attacks, spells or skills. all your units gets lethal damage bonus from stats. lethal damage bonus from weapons only stack with ur hero.|n- You can use edict with ur reputation, they can be requested into Ekrom castle's hall. duration is calculated by ingame hours. 1 game hour = 50 real seconds.|n- Hero attribute bonus from enchanted armors works as the following rule. (applies to AGI, STR and INT attrb):|n|cffffcc00"Increase bonus" = 15% bonus|r|n|cffffcc00"Strongly increase bonus" = 25% bonus|r|n|cffffcc00"Very strongly increase bonus" =  45% bonus|r|n-|cffffcc00Chests & vaults drop|r: these items have value clasification (1- 9 ). and their value means dice throws  for drop event. Low level units drops low value chests, each throw has 33% gems & potions chance, 10% scroll chance and 9% equipment chance. 
