STRING 8563
// Items: I0LH (About Armors), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
There are 5 armor type per class. every armor has 21 variations from "Increased  some stat" to "Triple Very Increased Some Stats". Armors are dropped by monsters and can be bought from armors shop. Armors variations are called "Enchanted armors" and be sold by the Tinker hero in Valdivia city. The armor defense bonus is multiplied by 4 when you equip some class armor. example if you see +12 armor bonus, the real defense is +48 armor. only work with class.
}

