STRING 8566
// Items: I0LI (About Weapons), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
There are 12 weapons type per class: 12 Swords, 12 Axes, etc. You can equip two weapons, or Weapon + shield. Sword has lethal strike default abilty, dagger has Attack speed ability, Axe has mutilate default abilty and Staff have magic effect ability. (bows are not completed).
}

