STRING 8572
// Items: I0M8 (About Sets), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
Sets are introduced to help us to keep other extra abilties to confront the 6 slots restriction inventory. Move speed, HP regen, mana regen, extra stats and some others can be suplied in one item when you complete the set. From now set are relative to clothes. currently active set is the bear set. (check warrior info to get more advice about bear set). Set works as recipes. all sets have 4 parts.
}

