STRING 8613
// Items: I0MB (Enthashara Story I), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
...A kingdom without king...|nIn a land of magic and mystery, a kingdom falls asleep under an unknown power. A kingdom without a king. The last king, the wise Albert, died by a strange sick and the heir to the throne, Prince Valkan is lost.
The voices in the chaos, say the rumor about a rare force of undead coming from the south, and both the day and night seem to say that nature cries the wounds that those undeads leave behind.|nIf the prince returns ...
gloriously he would command the final war against the undead invasion.
... Where is he?.. Is he really dead, as Henry thinks?
And what about you?  where will tilt your heart? What might you choose?
}

