STRING 8616
// Items: I0MC (Enthashara Story II), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
Leading Enthashara (whose capital is Ekrom) three forces fight for the kingdom control.|nThe first force |cffffcc00The Ekrom Army|r is led by Baron Henry, and his songs says that they are the legitimate defenders of the kingdom.|nThe second force |cffffcc00The Wolf's fang Brotherhood|r is home to people called rebels. They are declared Valkan main supporters, and expect a return to claim the throne. Nothing indicates about if their loyalty is true.|nThe third force |cffffcc00The Ancient Core of Enthashara|r  former home of sages and arcane mages always have declared themselves neutral, but the voices says some of their hearts are corrupted in the middle of the essence.|nThere is another force, a force that has never been known, only fables tell about this force |cffffcc00The Black Hand Brotherhood|r. Some people believe that they are behind the undead invasion but at this time nothing can be true and nothing can be false.
}

