// Items: I0FB (Call Restitution), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
|cffadff2fTo start a new reassignation your hero mustn't wear any item.|r|nInvokes the power of Chronoss servant to reassign your stat points into a new distribution. For example typing:|cffffcc00-set str|r |cffff3333xxxx|r, 'xxxx' means amount of points to assign. You mustn't exceed the original stat limit. To finish a new assignation you must type |cffffcc00-set done|r then the prepared assignation will be activated. To restart a wrong assignation you must type|cff7cfc00 -set reset|r. To make this distribution permanently you must type -save after tested new assignations. Effect duration 1 entire game.|nCommand list:|n|cffffcc00-set str xxxx|n-set agi xxxx|n-set int xxxx|n-set frt xxx|n-set msr xxx|n-set cns xxx|r|nMaximun assignation for basic stat is 1200. for advanced stat is 900. |n|cffcd853f[VERY IMPORTANT] You cannot take reassignation if your hero is on altered state (drunken). |r
}

