STRING 9824
{
|cffffd700-new|r = creates a new character|n|cffffd700-save|r = saves character, inventory and soul inventory|n|cffffd700-load|r = loads saved character|n|cffffd700-ms|r = shows character's movespeed|n|cffffd700-wide|r = Setup camera to exploration zoom|n|cffffd700-rpg|r = enables RPG camera|n|cffffd700-zi|r = zoom in current camera|n|cffffd700-zo|r = zoom out current camera|n|cffffd700-cu|r = increases camera to up view|n|cffffd700-cd|r = decreases camera to down view|n|cffffd700-cr|r = rotates camera to right|n|cffffd700-cl|r = rotates camera to left|n|cffffd700-nor|r = normalize camera|n|cffffd700-leavepvp|r = works if you are alone in the pvp|n|cffffd700-clear|r = cleans text messages from your screen|n|cffffd700-repick|r = allows to repick a character (only one time per game)|n|cffffd700-suicide|r = Kills your hero. Usefull for unstuck.|n|cffffd700-dice|r = Rolls the dice|n|cffffd700-rules|r = Show rules for current clash call|n
}

