STRING 9835
// Items: I0LJ (About Shields), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
There are 12 Shield type. they are a very good option if you dont have a lot of hit points. they helps your defense. very good option for healers, mages and warrior. archer cannot equip shield.
}

STRING 9836
// Items: I0M9 (About Class Evolution), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
After you got some class, when you complete |cffffd700900 kills|r. you can take a new test promotion: the second class where you must choose a faction. There are 3 factions in game where you can fight.On the next update, the quests will be classified by factions. To get the next class, you must survive to the factions test. every faction has a ability bonus. Ancient Core has Mana bonus. Wolffangs has|cffffd700 Attack damage bonus|r, Ekrom Army has |cff87ceebHealth bonus|r. At this point, you need a good equipment  and decent level to take factions quest.
}

STRING 9837
// Items: I0MA (lastupdate), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
|cff716f64- Inserted Anticheat to stop some known cheats.|n- Fixed a lot of bugs and issues.|n|r|cff696969- Changed amount of Enchanted armor effect.|r|n|nVisit our site in facebook for the entire log about this update.
}

