STRING 9840
// Items: I0U5 (What to do?), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
Hi new player, from now you are a new warrior in the land of |cffadff2fEnthashara|r. Your journey starts in |cffadff2fEmerald Port|r. Basically your |cffffff00main target |ris the chosen of  |cffffff00character class|r, to complete all challenges  those come in your way. For this mission the leveling experience isn't enought so, you must |cffffff00kill|r some certain |cffffff00number|r of |cffffff00monsters|r to reach the |cff9acd32Class Requeriments|r. For example, reaching to first class you need |cff9d9da1300 kills|r. In your way you have two main helpers. A |cffffff00Soul guard|r|cffbbb7c7 |r(wisp), that works of an |cff9d9da1extra inventory |rand some items use and Your |cffffff00familiar|r, like a pet that you can rent for Familiar master, and works as |cff9d9da1defender slave|r, Every class has |cffffff003 evolutions |rand you must choose a |cffffff00Faction|r  that you'll defend. In Enthashara you'll find others interesting stuffs like forge. Enjoy it.|n|nAvahor
}

STRING 9841
// Items: I0A8 (Druid Info), Ubertip (Tooltip - Extended)
{
Druid is a skilled spiritual warrior. Main Attribute:INT. His active abilities are |cffffcc00Banish|r, |cffffcc00Healing Wave, Force of nature and Acid bomb|r. |nOnly male novices are allowed to take Druid test.|nWhen you complete 300 kills, you must talk with the druid into the Velhilmen's tavern. he will say that you need travel to Ekrom, and offer a gift to the Ancient World, a gem of each type, 5 gems in total. |cffffcc00Click here to see where is the Druid.|r
}

